{"tid":899282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼青年竟流行喝「水煮M巾」 當毒品　官方嚴打","createTime":"2018-11-12T10:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T10:41:19.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0e7dc2dba79b2a6eaf7e74460e61868b73d7d0e8","tid":899282,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T10:09:45.000Z","msg":"印尼流行一種噁心又不可思議的新毒品，當地青年竟然用水烹煮廢棄的衛生棉製毒服用，當局嚴打這股歪風，拘捕多人。<br />\n <br />\n新加坡「8頻道」、《海峽時報》等媒體報導，印尼青年興起在垃圾堆中翻撿衛生棉，服用煮過衛生棉的水，雖然聽起來很不衞生，但印尼國家緝毒局的官員敘普蘭納托（<br />\nSuprinarto）解釋，衛生棉水含有氯氣（chlorine），所產生的感覺與毒品相似。<br />\n <br />\n據稱此現象早在2016年已出現，當年印尼邦加勿裏洞（Bangka Belitung Island）和西爪哇（West Java）的年青人也有人仿傚，但不知起源。<br />\n <br />\n當地警方已經在雅加達、西爪哇和中爪哇等地，拘捕了多名用類似方法吸毒的青年。但目前未有足夠的法律條文，足以提出起訴。除了水煮衛生棉，亦有青年濫用防蚊液和咳嗽藥水。"},{"pid":"6b850a6ea0cc7d2321cf84e35ef808fabea80cf1","tid":899282,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T10:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5807b9dd5b5b369239cdd086cf23c9f127b8788","tid":899282,"uid":170365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母今次發達啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b957a221049e135a3ceb2f5d87e1c04fabdb846","tid":899282,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T10:11:33.000Z","msg":"好噁心"},{"pid":"5059ac47b21ede6b8fa4a8bc71eb147df1d53b1c","tid":899282,"uid":22365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T10:13:20.000Z","msg":"金寶氯水發達喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56fda348162510671009261a28aa1c5565255f7","tid":899282,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T10:22:39.000Z","msg":"東南亞國家都係低質啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5af09f1fa451b41ebd17b5ebf6435ed1edfbd98","tid":899282,"uid":46587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T10:31:34.000Z","msg":"終於明白點解塊西可以當八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a95d5a91db5c752fb1009392d6766fb0d4656ec","tid":899282,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T10:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yX5Rae0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyX5Rae0.png&h=3ed7c9f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"869c98f1a9d7e7ae0fda999cb1c6a92586344fc1","tid":899282,"uid":50310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T10:41:19.000Z","msg":"失傳已久的 採陰補陽<br />\n但我頂唔順<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}